# React管理后台模板

经典管理后台模板  

React全家桶(react-router,react-redux,@reduxjs/toolkit) + Typescript +Vite + Antd + tailwindcss  

******

## 技术栈

* React@18.2.x
* react-router@6.21.x
* react-redux@9.0.x
* @reduxjs/toolkit@2.0.x
* vite@5.0.x
* antd@5.12.x
* tailwindcss@3.4.x
* typescript
* eslint/tslint
* prettier
* stylelint
* sass

******

## 运行

```javascript
npm:
  npm install
  npm run dev
yarn:
  yarn
  yarn dev
```
